text: Cláudio Biekarck is a retired sailor from Brazil. Biekarck competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics, the 1976 Summer Olympics and the 1980 Summer Olympics. He was born on 16 May 1951.Cláudio Biekarck == References == Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Sailors Category:Olympians for Brazil Category:Sportspeople from São Paulo
